      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "ATAH kidashta et yom hashvi-i lishmecha,\ntachlit maaseih shamayim vaaretz.\nUveirachto mikol hayamim,\nv'kidashto mikol haz'manim,\nv'chein katuv b'Toratecha:\nVAY'CHULU hashamayim v'haaretz\nv'chol tz'vaam. Vay'chal Elohim bayom\nhashvi-i m'lachto asher asah,\nvayishbot bayom hashvi-i mikol\nm'lachto asher asah. Vay'varech\nElohim et yom hashvi-i vay'kadeish oto,\nki vo shavat mikol m'lachto\nasher bara Elohim laasot.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-15T15:04:08.353Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "xyRM0JS2uzT6MwCE3pQ2"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F189bce48-e52f-44ee-8d1f-2ea21ceaf4a5.jp2/416,370,1621,2194/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
      "id": "606cf621-1687-471e-8d14-366f06685e62",
      "target": {
        "source": "mishkan:page:189bce48-e52f-44ee-8d1f-2ea21ceaf4a5",
        "type": "SpecificResource",
        "selector": {
          "type": "FragmentSelector",
          "conformsTo": "http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/",
          "value": "xywh=pixel:433.89473684210526,2576.3157894736837,3560.5263157894733,961.052631578948"
        }
      },
      "@context": "http://www.w3.org/ns/anno.jsonld",
      "type": "Annotation",
      "body": [
        {
          "type": "TextualBody",
          "purpose": "transcribing",
          "value": "YOU SET ASIDE the seventh day for Your Name, the pinnacle of Creation; and\nYou blessed it above all other days, more sacred than all Festival times. So it is\nwritten in Your Torah: The heaven and the earth were finished and all their array.\nOn the seventh day, God had completed the work that had been done, ceasing then\non the seventh day from all the work that [God] had done. Then God blessed the\nseventh day and made it holy, and ceased from all the creative work that God [had\nchosen] to do.",
          "language": "en"
        }
      ],
      "created": "2026-07-15T15:04:18.278Z",
      "creator": {
        "isGuest": true,
        "id": "xyRM0JS2uzT6MwCE3pQ2"
      },
      "image_url": "https://momoiro.hallyu.io/mishkan/iiif/3/mishkan%2F189bce48-e52f-44ee-8d1f-2ea21ceaf4a5.jp2/433,2576,3560,961/max/0/default.jpg"
    },
    {
      "id": "ae562020-8244-4c8e-972b-1949bd007a72",
      "target": {
